	   <tr><td colspan=2>As for the Veeshan faction, I wasn't aware that the GD giants gave Veeshan faction. I was under the impression they gave only Coldain faction. If that's so, then by all means live at the Giant Fort in GD for a while. Remember, you get a very small faction hit from greens, so concentrate on blues and higher. <br><br>I don't know your level, but if you are of a level to group in the Kael Arena, that's the best and fastest way to raise your Veeshan faction. I went from Dubious to Ally in about 10 hours in the Arena. The giants in Wakening Land outside the Kael entrance area also give Veeshan faction. If your level is too low to hunt in the Arena, then you can definitely get faster faction there than in GD.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
