	   <tr><td colspan=2>I'm a lvl 10 druid and confused about ALL the spells I have. I'd like to know which ones are the best to use and how to use them. Thanks!<br>Shely<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
