	   <tr><td colspan=2>Greetings,<br><br>Not being high enough level yet to use those spells, but having an interest in trade skills, I'd heard of them.<br><br>Imbued plains pebbles are ingredients in items usable by those who worship Karana, and imbued emeralds are ingredients in items usable by those who worship Tunare.<br><br>For a full list of deities/gems/items look at:<br> <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/secrets/imbued_gemlist.htm" target=_new>http://www.eqtraders.com/secrets/imbued_gemlist.htm</a><br><br>Hope this is some help.<br><br><br>Fight on!<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Kelanthor<br>Wood Elf Druid of the 41st Circle<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=212672" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=212672</a></td></tr>
