	   <tr><td colspan=2>You didn't mention your level, so I'm not sure where to direct you in the event that you would like to farm the item yourself instead of purchasing it. <br><br>For tunic, I recommend a Shroud of Nature :&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>AC: +13 Wis: +6 Fire Resist: +8 Cold Resist: +8  <br>This drops off a level 36-40 mob in the Temple of Droga. At least until you can get some Planes or Temple of Veeshan armor. The best in the game, in my opinion, is Elyssian Armor, but that stuff is way too expensive to buy. <br><br>As for a weapon, until I received my epic, I didn't bother with one. I recommend a Paw of Opalla in your main hand and a Charred Guardian Shield in your off hand. Those two together will give you +18 wisdom. <br><br>In my range slot, I carry a Seal of Thordain: <br>AC: +3 Wis: +3 Int: +3 Magic Resist: +3 Cold Resist: +3 Mana: +30 Free as a benefit from the Prayer Shawl Quest.  Again, not sure of your level, but it's not that much trouble to get the Seal. You only need to go to the 3rd or 4th shawl to get it.<br><br>For your belt, I suggest a Crystalline belt; <br>AC: +5 Agi: +3 Wis: +3 HP: +10 .  Drops in Crystal Caverns in Velious.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
